##NIRFAST matlab installation (windows and ubuntu)
Download Nirfast from http://www.nirfast.org
Unzip Nirfast onto your computer where you would like it to be installed
Open Matlab, and go to File -> Set Path -> Add With Subfolders
Select the Nirfast folder, then Save and Close

##NIRFASTSlicer installation (Ubuntu)
Download Nirfastslicer from http://www.nirfast.org
Unzip Nirfastslicer onto your computer
Open unzipped file and right click the mouse in that directory and select open in terminal option
In terminal window type ./NIRFASTSlicer and then enter
